      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Offered here is an exceptional vehicle in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find for the discerning buyer. This car is in showroom state, both mechanically and aesthetically, with a flawless exterior and an interior that still looks and smells brand new. It has been meticulously cared for, stored in a climate-controlled environment, and comes with a full, documented service history. Every feature works perfectly, and the driving experience is as smooth as the day it first left the factory. This is the ideal choice for someone seeking a vehicle in pristine, collector-grade condition.",
