    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for functionality over aesthetics. While the engine and transmission are in working order, the car shows its age with some visible interior wear and minor exterior scuffs. You should expect some small fluid leaks typical of a vehicle this age, but it remains a solid choice for someone needing reliable transportation on a budget.",
