    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride that\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. I've taken good care of it, and it's ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
