      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission paired with a variable M-differential lock for precise power delivery. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive double VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis has been inspected for subframe fatigue to ensure structural rigidity. While the exterior exhibits honest road-going patina consistent with its age, the suspension kinematics remain tight and the 8,000 RPM redline remains visceral. This is a driver-focused specimen with sorted internals and exceptional analog feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
