    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly balances performance and practicality. This car has served as a reliable daily driver, and I have maintained a comprehensive folder of all service receipts, including a recent professional multi-point inspection and fluid flush. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, though keen eyes will notice minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the door handle\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is in great shape, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, including the dual-zone climate control, premium audio system, and all safety sensors, is fully operational. It handles beautifully with no vibrations or unusual noises. This is an honest, solid vehicle that is ready for many more miles of worry-free driving.",
      "price": 31500.0,
